task.summary: Fixed bug where headers from CryptoPP-Cmake were not getting included.
Seperated CryptoPP-Cmake and CVT cloning stages and fixed bugs that were caused when leaving these two stages together. + Did some better documenting. + some other stuff....
Fixed a typo and removed the "MESSAGE("CVT")" used for debug/testing the CmakeLists.txt
Started embedding lz4 and zlib in libSDP. + Some other small edits.
Added Zlib's license file. + Added Zlib's .c files to CMakeLists.txt
Deleted un-needed stuff in the contrib folder.
Continued migration and fixed zconf.h generation.
Continued working on migration. Migrated Hex->Bin/Bin->Hex functions + placed them in a separate class for convenience.
Continued working on migration. Continued cryptstreambuf migration block cipher -> block cipher / stream cipher modes. + bunch of other stuff...
Continued working on migration. Continued cryptstreambuf migration block cipher -> block cipher / stream cipher modes. + bunch of other stuff...
Changed CmakeLists.txt to use library from submodule.
Made zlib an external dependency + made external dependency path checking more efficient.
